org.mobicents.slee.enabler.sip
Interface SubscriptionClientChild

All Known Subinterfaces:
SubscriptionClientChildSbbLocalObject
All Known Implementing Classes:
SubscriptionClientChildSbb
public interface SubscriptionClientChild

An application enabler, which may be used to integrate SIP Subscription Client functionality into a SLEE application. The enabler supports subscribing state with respect to single and list resources.

Author:
baranowb, martins
